    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うう……なんだかそわそわしてきちゃった\nいよいよ始まっちゃうんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughhh… I’m getting kinda nervous!\nIt’s finally gonna start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.866666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 8.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね\nそして、その一回戦目は、トリエル対リズノワ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.\nAnd the first match is TRINITYAiLE against LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 14.966666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どっちも、負けてほしくない\nでも、どっちが勝っても辛いライブバトルになりそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want either team to lose.\nBut‚ no matter which team wins‚ it’s gonna be a fierce concert battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 21.766666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん\nけど私ね、正直ワクワクもしてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nI’ll have to admit though‚ I’m excited as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの凄さもリズノワの凄さも\n私達、うんと近くで見てきたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve seen up close just how amazing\nboth TRINITYAiLE and LizNoir are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "だから、そんなリズノワとトリエルが戦うんなら\nきっとすっごいステージになるって思えるんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If LizNoir and TRINITYAiLE are going up against each other‚\nI’m sure it’s going to be an incredible performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 45.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……うん。私も同感\n最後までしっかり、見届けないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I agree.\nWe’ll need to see what happens until the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4200.000000000003,
          "startTime": 49.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 49.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_thrx-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 49.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お疲れ様……あら？　美帆子だけなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello… Oh? Is it just you‚ Mihoko?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "franとkanaも呼んでいたはずだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought I asked Fran and Kana to be here as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 58
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、姫野さん\n来ないと思いますよ。二人とも興味なさそうでしたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ Ms. Himeno.\nI doubt they’re coming. Neither of them seems very interested.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "思います、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You “doubt” it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "貴方達、連絡は取り合っていないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren’t you in contact with each other?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 70.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "私達がお互いの連絡先、交換していると思います？\n姫野さんの所にも来てないんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you really think we’ve exchanged contact info?\nThey haven’t contacted you‚ I take it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 78
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええ。それじゃあの子達、オフを取ったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I guess they decided to take the day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日は出演も取材もないから、別にいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not that it matters since you don’t have any appearances or interviews.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まあ、いいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh well‚ never mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "貴方としては、今回の初戦のカード、どう見る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "what’s your take on the match card for the first round?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 92.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 92.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。どちらも実力は同程度ですから\nかなりの接戦になるんじゃないか、と思ってます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see. It’ll be a close race\nas both teams are of a similar caliber.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、どちらが順当に勝ち上がってきたとしても\nさほど警戒する相手ではないかと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In any case‚ I wouldn’t worry too much\nabout whichever of the two comes out on top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 108.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "彼女達の実力は、私達には遠く及びませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both trail far behind us when it comes to abilities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自信があるのは結構だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It‘s all well and good to be confident‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "舐めてかかると足下すくわれるわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but if you’re not careful‚ you might be in for a surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 119.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ここに来ているから、美帆子はあの二人とは違って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I pegged you as being more circumspective than the other two‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "思慮深い方だと思っていたけど……違ったかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "since you’re here now… Was I wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 127.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "あの人達と一緒にしないで下さい\n私はただ、客観的な事実を述べただけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t compare me with them.\nI’m just stating objective facts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 130.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ちゃんと思慮深く観察しているつもりですよ\n実力は私達の方が上でも、いずれは戦うだろう相手",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ in my own way‚ I am being circumspective.\nThey may trail us in abilities‚ but we’ll compete against them sooner or later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 145.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_04-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "油断なんてしません。たかが火の粉程度でも\nちゃんと払い方を学んで備えますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t let my guard down. Whether or not they put up much of a fight‚\nI’ll do my research and be ready to take them out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう……ふふっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Heheh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "なんだかんだで、貴方も本当、面白い子よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ you really are a fascinating girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
